element.name: killeek by Windsockers, Multi-cache (1/1.5)

center.p: Killeek church dates from the 1700's and is built in a Medieval graveyard taught to date between 1500-1700

long-description.p:
At the above location take note of the number of Keelings layed to rest here call this number A
Note the number of men call this B
Note the number of women call this C
The cache can be found at N53 27.18(A+B) W6 16.A1C

The Cache is a micro container you'll need to byop.
Please don't remove the container from its location just open it to get the log and take care to rehide the cache to prevent muggles from discovering its location.
